==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unfathered
<hw>Un*fa"thered</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Having no father; fatherless; hence, born contrary to nature.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Having no acknowledged father; hence, illegitimate;
spurious; bastard.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unfavorable</ent>⟦br⟧
